title: Fritz!Box Traffic
description:
"Fritz!Box Traffic" is a Sidebar Gadget for Vista/Windows 7/8/8.1/10. 

The Tool uses UPnP to download current trafficdata from the Fritzbox and displays these. 

The .gadget file is for sidebar-view.

Extended Settings can be found by double-clicking onto the "Fritz!Box Traffic Settings" title of the settings window while pressing shift.

Using the msi-setup on win10 a taskbar deskband to display the data can be installed.

 
Gadget Version: 
Version 1.11.94
FritzBoxTraffic11194.gadget

Applikation: 
Version 1.11.94
FritzBoxTraffic-0.11.176.zip

Applikation Setup + "Deskband Fritz!Box Traffic" for the Taskbar (only Win10): 
Version 1.11.94
FritzBoxTrafficSetup-64bit-1.11.94.msi
FritzBoxTrafficSetup-32bit-1.11.94-2.msi


For "Deskband Fritz!BoxTraffic" die Microsoft Visual C++ 2015 Redistributable must be installed.

German version of this text can be found on: www.bawe.eu
